ed for almost a year through the desert, but that he got more tired when he had to walk through the streets of Tangier buying his leather.\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "It was the language of enthusiasm, of things accomplished with love and purpose, and as part of a search for something believed in and desired."), mdx("p", null, "When someone makes a decision, he is really diving into a strong current that will carry him to places he had never dreamed of when he first made the decision."), mdx("p", null, "people need not fear the unknown if they are capable of achieving what they need and want."), mdx("p", null, "So he could not be hasty, nor impatient. If he pushed forward impulsively, he would fail to see the signs and omens left by God along his path."), mdx("p", null, "\u2018Eat when it\u2019s time to eat. And move along when it\u2019s time to move along.\u2019\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "At that moment, it seemed to him that time stood still, and the Soul of the World surged within him."), mdx("p", null, "Actually, it wasn\u2019t that those things, in themselves, revealed anything at all; it was just that people, looking at what was occurring around them, could find a means of penetration to the Soul of the World."), mdx("p", null, "If you pay attention to the present, you can improve upon it. And, if you improve on the present, what comes later will also be better. Forget about the future, and live each day according to the teachings, confident that God loves his children. Each day, in itself, brings with it an eternity.\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "to die tomorrow was no worse than dying on any other day. Every day was there to be lived or to mark one\u2019s departure from this world. Everything depended on one word: \u201CMaktub.\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "\u201CCourage is the quality most essential to understanding the Language of the World.\u201D"), mdx("p", null, "\u201CWhen a person really desires something, all the universe conspires to help that person to realize hi